      "title": "Merchandise export earnings rise over USD 1,100 Mn in July: EDB",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Earnings from the merchandise exports increased by 2.25 % y-o-y to USD 1,128.7 million in July 2022 as per the data released by the Sri Lanka Customs, the Export Development Board (EDB) says.",
        "This was mainly due to the increase in earnings from export of Apparel & Textiles."
